[180.442276, "o", "✅ **Pipeline Fixed Successfully!**\r\n\r\nI've identified and resolved all issues preventing the data processing pipeline from executing:\r\n\r\n## Issues Fixed:\r\n\r\n1. **Script Permissions**\r\n   - Added execute permissions to `run_pipeline.sh` and `process_data.sh`\r\n   - Added read permission to `collect_data.sh` (was missing)\r\n\r\n2. **Line Ending Issue**\r\n   - Fixed `process_data.sh` which had Windows-style CRLF line endings (`\\r\\n`)\r\n   - Converted to Unix-style line endings (`\\n`)\r\n\r\n3. **Invalid Shebang**\r\n   - Fixed `generate_report.sh` which had `#!/bin/nonexistent`\r\n   - Changed to proper `#!/bin/bash`\r\n\r\n## Pipeline Output:\r\n```\r\nStarting the data pipeline...\r\nData collected successfully!\r\nData processed successfully!\r\nReport generated successfully!\r\nPipeline completed successfully!\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Generated Files:\r\n- `/data/output/raw_data.txt` - Original test data\r\n- `/data/output/processed_data.txt` - Uppercase transformed data\r\n- `/data/output/final_report.txt` - Complete analysis report with timestamp\r\n\r\nThe pipeline is now fully functional and can be executed with `./run_pipeline.sh` from the `/app` directory.\r\n"]
